{"tid":767340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩人中暑亡　西班牙氣溫或破48℃","createTime":"2018-08-04T11:46:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-04T14:13:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8977fa6463736d87ce947c2b8ddd395e9cc3cc7c","tid":767340,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T11:46:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180804/20468517\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180804%2F20468517&d=pTHOzgs83DC2iwcnw2hHS8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=0c777bff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180804%2F20468517&h=e69a7ede\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180804/20468517</a><br />\n<br />\n兩人中暑亡　西班牙氣溫或破48℃<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180804/large/a1305a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180804%2Flarge%2Fa1305a.gif&h=43852dab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■巴塞隆拿民眾到海邊消暑。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n北非一股熱空氣侵襲西班牙及葡萄牙，令兩國氣溫飆升至40℃以上，料未來數日天氣會更酷熱，甚或會打破歐洲史上48℃的紀錄。熱浪令西班牙有兩人中暑死亡，德國亦有國家公園爆發山火。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n葡萄牙45.2℃<br />\n<br />\n葡萄牙首都里斯本前日錄得45.2℃高溫，居民帕斯庫亞爾指，「里斯本今周末會成為世界上最熱的城市之一。現在才是早上10時就已經太熱了，實在難以忍受」。天氣預報指，南部城市的氣溫周末飆升至47℃，達該國歷年最高溫紀錄。鑑於去年的山火造成了114人死亡，當局特別提高對山火的警覺。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙多地錄40℃以上的高溫，當局發出熱浪警告，並預料未來數日的氣溫會達44℃。當地有一名48歲正在道路上工作的工人，以及一名78歲正下田的老翁中暑身亡。<br />\n<br />\n炎熱乾燥的天氣亦使德國東部的薩克森瑞士國家公園爆發山火。該區濃煙密佈，火勢不斷蔓延，山火面積達4,000平方米，暫未威脅民居。當局出動140人滅火，並指「火災發生於一些很難到達的位置」，消防員要由攀山拯救隊及爬山專家陪同，利用繩索到達火場。<br />\n<br />\n路透社  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n安理會移除對北韓人道援助障礙"},{"pid":"6e1a0c718bb821f9cf7aa575ec259ef60f56dba6","tid":767340,"uid":113626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T11:48:55.000Z","msg":"大自然發則邊有得避免<br />\n一係好似鄰國咁, 個個都唔駛(唔想)死<br />\n咪爆到十幾億人囉"},{"pid":"8fae8b5307e7ae08509fdf6de1a210c38447c43f","tid":767340,"uid":132587,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T11:50:53.000Z","msg":"痴線一年比一年熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28c806e8235bf3b071a1e27e20abd0af7d8c2760","tid":767340,"uid":38456,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T11:52:30.000Z","msg":"反暖化撚係邊"},{"pid":"cd4221e94d825c54e0b07aaaf6d2a857e724502f","tid":767340,"uid":46328,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T11:54:02.000Z","msg":"暖化撚又勝一仗"},{"pid":"cb1e239b684e52350f2b240d27a662bf324068d6","tid":767340,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T12:26:02.000Z","msg":"窮到無錢開冷氣"},{"pid":"f4b04da182ce32011062bec2628fa632f503d3c9","tid":767340,"uid":503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T12:31:24.000Z","msg":"岩岩離開馬德里<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係地獄級熱"},{"pid":"0d0724a258b950a97810faa44ab22d22a373fd77","tid":767340,"uid":45518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T12:34:52.000Z","msg":"暖化撚可以專心喺度討論而不被騷擾"},{"pid":"71e3370836006fc6a0c4fdb7dd7173f55ab85da5","tid":767340,"uid":52358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T12:35:46.000Z","msg":"熱/凍 - 全球暖化撚:反全球暖化撚又縮返入老母個閪度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔熱/唔凍 - 反全球暖化撚:全球暖化撚又縮返入老母個閪度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無限loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c78a7d1b9f80b6e9514e3108dbc2b7b21a81d77c","tid":767340,"uid":183491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T12:39:31.000Z","msg":"又要開大冷氣了"},{"pid":"a18c7355c3c35180f8c4fcfcea93b21ed95a5cd2","tid":767340,"uid":132038,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy